"{\n  \"correct\": \"no\",\n  \"explanation\": \"The DateFormatter and MonthLocator are being used together but the DateFormatter will override any custom date tick labels set by set_xticklabels. Also, setting custom ticks with set_xticks and then using a MonthLocator will cause the ticks to be reset. To fix this, either use the DateFormatter and MonthLocator together or use custom tick labels.\",\n  \"patch\": \"17d17\\n< ax.set_xticks(df.date.unique())\\n< ax.set_xticklabels(labels=df.date.unique(), rotation=45)\\n\"\n}"